snippet.title: Sunkenland - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Sunkenland is a survival game themed around Waterworld. Explore sunken cities, build your base, craft items, trade and fight pirates as you struggle to survive in an aquatic post-apocalypse world plagued by hunger and violence. Take on what remains on the ocean floor alone or with a friend in co-op. Sunkenland is launching into Early Access in Summer 2023 for PC.

#Sunkenland #SurvivalGame
